Terms.s2Content:
The Platform is a technological service that enables interaction between users for concluding transactions in respect of digital goods.

The Operator:

is not a seller or buyer of goods;
is not a financial institution;
does not provide payment or banking services;
does not hold users' funds or crypto assets.

The Platform only provides technical processing of transactions related to the performance of deals.

Terms.s3Content:
Users may enter into transactions in respect of:

digital in-game items;
game currency;
accounts;
game-related services.

The Operator does not guarantee the lawfulness of use of digital assets in video games and is not liable for sanctions imposed by third parties.

Terms.s6Content:
In the course of performing a deal, the Platform may temporarily hold crypto assets for technical purposes solely to secure performance of the deal.

Such holding:

is not an asset custody service;
is limited in time;
is carried out only in the framework of the specific transaction.

Terms.s7Content:
The Operator is entitled to charge a commission for use of the Platform.

The commission may include:

commission on conclusion of a deal;
commission on payment processing;
commission on payouts.

Terms.s8Content:
The Platform may require users to undergo identification procedures.

Identification may be carried out through third-party partners.

The user agrees to the transfer of personal data to partners to the extent necessary to comply with legal requirements.

User must complete identity verification (KYC) before performing financial operations beyond test transactions. Verification includes:
• identity confirmation (passport/ID card/driver's license);
• proof of address (utility bill or bank statement);
• current selfie with document to verify face matches document;
• other requirements in accordance with applicable law.

Failure to comply with these requirements may result in blocking of access to the Platform's financial functions.

Terms.s9Content:
The Platform may:

block suspicious transactions;
suspend payouts;
require additional identity verification.

Terms.s11Content:
Users are prohibited from:

using stolen accounts;
manipulating transactions;
money laundering;
violating the law.

Terms.s12Content:
The Operator is not liable for:

users' actions;
blocking of accounts in video games;
loss of digital assets;
technical failures of third parties.

