CookiePolicy.s3Content:
Our Platform may use cookies set by third parties, including:

• Payment and crypto providers — to process transactions, verify payments, and secure checkout flows;
• Authentication providers (e.g. Google) — to enable sign-in features;
• Analytics services — to measure usage and improve the Platform;
• Security and fraud prevention services — to protect users and detect suspicious activity.

Third-party cookies are essential for crypto and payment operations. They enable secure authentication, transaction verification, and compliance with regulatory requirements. By using the Platform, you acknowledge that these third-party cookies may be placed on your device.

CookiePolicy.s4Content:
You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to:

• Block all cookies;
• Block third-party cookies only;
• Delete existing cookies.

Please note: blocking essential or security cookies may prevent the Platform from functioning correctly. You may not be able to log in, complete transactions, or use payment features if essential cookies are disabled.

CookiePolicy.s5Content:
By continuing to use the Platform, you consent to our use of cookies in accordance with this policy.

You may withdraw or change your consent at any time by:

• Adjusting your browser settings to block or delete cookies;
• Using any cookie preference tools we provide on the Platform;
• Contacting us via the Contact us page.

We will respect your preferences. Note that withdrawing consent for essential cookies may limit or prevent your use of the Platform.
